snippet: The Larstrand is expected to be completed by the end of next year, joining two other high-priced luxury rentals in the neighborhood.
abstract: Larstrand, upscale residential building offering 181 rental units, is being developed on the Upper West Side by Friedland Properties and Rose Associates; building is expected to be completed by the end of 2013, joining two other high-priced luxury rentals in the area.
lead_paragraph: The Larstrand is expected to be completed by the end of next year, joining two other high-priced luxury rentals in the neighborhood.

headline.seo: Along With the Larstrand, Pricey Rentals Rise on the Upper West Side
headline.main: Another Pricey Rental Rises on the Upper West Side
